{% schema %}
  {
    
    "name": "Section 3",
    "tag": "section",
    "class": "gps-572511850856711392 gps gpsil",
    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/smooth-spine/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=572511850722231520&sectionId=572511850856711392)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggc9AgGhBaX_text","label":"ggc9AgGhBaX_text","default":"<p>Home &gt; Pain Relief &gt; Sciatica</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg18fnVh9FH_text","label":"gg18fnVh9FH_text","default":"<strong>How This Grandma Finally Fixed Her Sciatica 'For Good' After Two Years Of Agony </strong>- Without Surgery, Pills, Or Diets"},{"type":"html","id":"gg3SZKcR-Fp_text","label":"gg3SZKcR-Fp_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(255, 191, 0, 0);\">If you're struggling with stabbing pain,</span> tightness, or tingling in your back or legs, read this short article right now before you try anything else.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggmYAZDN3lo_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggmYAZDN3lo_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-5bf8297a-9c56-4d2d-bc80-2f1c2ef7f9c7.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggHpXq6PXJb_text","label":"ggHpXq6PXJb_text","default":"<p>3,791 Ratings</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggyOm7qn9eJ_youtubeUrl","label":"ggyOm7qn9eJ_youtubeUrl","default":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M"},{"type":"html","id":"ggyOm7qn9eJ_vimeoUrl","label":"ggyOm7qn9eJ_vimeoUrl","default":"https://vimeo.com/347119375"},{"type":"html","id":"ggyOm7qn9eJ_html5Url","label":"ggyOm7qn9eJ_html5Url","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/9c98f123e4a64a8bb8cea9b8d220bb81.mp4"},{"type":"html","id":"gg5W6iOkaU0_customText","label":"gg5W6iOkaU0_customText","default":"By Evelyn|"},{"type":"html","id":"ggk50N3Vywd_text","label":"ggk50N3Vywd_text","default":"<p>Hi, I'm Evelyn, and I want to share my journey with sciatica and relentless back pain, and how I finally found relief.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>For months, I was dealing with a constant ache in my lower back that turned into sharp, burning pain shooting down my leg.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Simple things like standing at the sink or walking to the mailbox became exhausting.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Sciatica pain was stealing the life I used to enjoy.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I tried everything - posture braces, stretching routines, heat pads, even painkillers my doctor prescribed.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>But nothing gave me lasting relief.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Each morning I woke up <strong>feeling more helpless and more afraid</strong> that this was just how the rest of my life would feel.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Keep reading, because I did find a solution - and I’m going to share it with you in just a moment…</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggtKkWj920i_text","label":"ggtKkWj920i_text","default":"My Sciatica Was So Bad I Couldn’t Stand, Sit, or Sleep Without Feeling Like My Spine Was on Fire…"},{"type":"html","id":"ggLFGG4SSCQ_youtubeUrl","label":"ggLFGG4SSCQ_youtubeUrl","default":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M"},{"type":"html","id":"ggLFGG4SSCQ_vimeoUrl","label":"ggLFGG4SSCQ_vimeoUrl","default":"https://vimeo.com/347119375"},{"type":"html","id":"ggLFGG4SSCQ_html5Url","label":"ggLFGG4SSCQ_html5Url","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/2588b58708ec41f99b77cf3c2b1e1f61.mp4"},{"type":"html","id":"ggtZSSr4Djc_text","label":"ggtZSSr4Djc_text","default":"<p>I never thought I’d be telling strangers what it felt like to crawl across the floor - but you need to understand just how bad my back pain had become.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Some mornings, I couldn’t even stand upright.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>My spine felt like it was collapsing in on itself, and <strong>the pain shooting down my legs was so intense I’d break out</strong> in a cold sweat just trying to move.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Even my daughter looked at me one morning and said, “Mom… this isn’t normal.”</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggA6F3xpugM_text","label":"ggA6F3xpugM_text","default":"The Hidden Cause of Sciatica and Back Pain That Most Doctors Miss"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQsB0hj91f_youtubeUrl","label":"ggQsB0hj91f_youtubeUrl","default":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQsB0hj91f_vimeoUrl","label":"ggQsB0hj91f_vimeoUrl","default":"https://vimeo.com/347119375"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQsB0hj91f_html5Url","label":"ggQsB0hj91f_html5Url","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/d1ff3458a11546a0b0717ed829d0cea4.mp4"},{"type":"html","id":"ggjq0bpAws4_text","label":"ggjq0bpAws4_text","default":"<p>After seeing how much I was struggling, my daughter told me about a strange back therapy she’d been doing at home…</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It came after her doctor told her the real reason for her sciatica…</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>And how most people are focusing on the wrong thing when trying to relieve sciatica and back pain…</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>It turns out the real problem with sciatica <u>all starts with the spinal discs…</u></strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>You see, those discs are supposed to act like shock absorbers - keeping space between your vertebrae and protecting the nerves that run through your spine.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>But as we age, those discs start to shrink, forcing your vertebrae closer together, pushing the discs out of place, and compressing the nerves</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Like a mattress that’s been slept on for too many years, they flatten out and stop supporting the structure above them.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Discs getting pushed out of place pinch the nerves, causing that burning, stabbing, or numbing pain in your back, hips, and legs.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>That’s why none of the solutions I tried ever worked.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>They were all focused on the symptoms, but they did nothing to relieve the compression or restore the spinal discs where the real problem was hiding.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggT6Xm4BV4u_text","label":"ggT6Xm4BV4u_text","default":"If You Don’t Restore Your Disc Height, The Pain Will Only Get Worse"},{"type":"html","id":"ggn-CGnN_Bf_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggn-CGnN_Bf_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-b7aa7053-3454-498a-beb4-449144decbc9.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggSag6O2AwP_text","label":"ggSag6O2AwP_text","default":"<p>If the space between your spinal discs isn’t restored, <strong>your vertebrae will keep collapsing</strong>, trapping the nerves that run through your back and legs.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The pressure builds, pinching those nerves tighter, and triggering the burning, stabbing, or numbing pain that <strong>makes walking, sitting, or even lying down unbearable.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Over time, your spine stiffens, your mobility fades, and the pain becomes more constant, setting off a cycle where even simple movements start to feel impossible.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I was terrified of where this was heading.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Would I lose the ability to move without help?</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Would I become stuck at home, watching life pass me by from a recliner?</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>But thankfully, there was hope…</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggdeViqKQt6_text","label":"ggdeViqKQt6_text","default":"The Solution That Changed My Life"},{"type":"html","id":"gggGNSQX-9r_youtubeUrl","label":"gggGNSQX-9r_youtubeUrl","default":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M"},{"type":"html","id":"gggGNSQX-9r_vimeoUrl","label":"gggGNSQX-9r_vimeoUrl","default":"https://vimeo.com/347119375"},{"type":"html","id":"gggGNSQX-9r_html5Url","label":"gggGNSQX-9r_html5Url","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/c16a82718c5b492ebb40d0f70a9f95a1.mp4"},{"type":"html","id":"ggCmh_il84F_text","label":"ggCmh_il84F_text","default":"<p>Thankfully, my daughter’s doctor had recommended an at-home solution that helped hundreds of his patients successfully <strong>relieve disc pressure and get real, lasting relief from sciatica and back pain after just a few sessions.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg8qpT8sjvc_text","label":"gg8qpT8sjvc_text","default":"<p>It’s called the SmoothSpine “Triple Fusion” Massager.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggK03kTunUI_text","label":"ggK03kTunUI_text","default":"<p>My daughter let me borrow hers, and I’ve been using it every day for just 15 minutes while lying down.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>The results?</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Truly life-changing.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>My lower back feels lighter, looser, and stronger.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I can sit without flinching, stand without bracing myself, and walk around the house without that stabbing nerve pain shooting down my leg.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>By the second day, I felt less stiff getting out of bed.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Now, the pain that used to take over my mornings is almost completely gone.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Once the pressure between my vertebrae started to ease up, it felt like my spine could finally breathe again.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>The discs had room to expand, the nerves weren’t being pinched anymore, and everything in my back just started working the way it’s supposed to.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggn0Kiy3vDa_text","label":"ggn0Kiy3vDa_text","default":"How SmoothSpine Triple Fusion Massager Works"},{"type":"html","id":"ggMLBTdkwz7_youtubeUrl","label":"ggMLBTdkwz7_youtubeUrl","default":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M"},{"type":"html","id":"ggMLBTdkwz7_vimeoUrl","label":"ggMLBTdkwz7_vimeoUrl","default":"https://vimeo.com/347119375"},{"type":"html","id":"ggMLBTdkwz7_html5Url","label":"ggMLBTdkwz7_html5Url","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/9e2fd1f201bb4d21a5ca86ab77b72611.mp4"},{"type":"html","id":"gglPNimzCf1_text","label":"gglPNimzCf1_text","default":"<p>I'm incredibly thankful to be on the road to recovery now by simply using SmoothSpine for 5 to 15 minutes per day from the comfort of my own home.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>I'm basically reversing what caused the issue in the first place, which is the thin collapsing discs in my spine.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggvfzP7Hf1I_text","label":"ggvfzP7Hf1I_text","default":"<p>The \"Triple Fusion\" massager uses three therapies to solve this right at the source:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggAN1eUXVtU_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggAN1eUXVtU_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-920fdecf-6aaa-4453-b723-169beceb7ffd.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gglbwd1ZED9_text","label":"gglbwd1ZED9_text","default":"<p><strong><u>Dynamic Traction Therapy</u> </strong>gently stretches and separates your vertebrae, reducing pressure on pinched nerves and allowing your spinal discs to rehydrate and regain their natural cushioning.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggAGi0kqAfU_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggAGi0kqAfU_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-184cb9c3-9e15-4403-abf0-814caf8cc63b.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggAGi0kqAfU_srcSet_tablet_src","label":"ggAGi0kqAfU_srcSet_tablet_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-184cb9c3-9e15-4403-abf0-814caf8cc63b.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_ve15hqdq_text","label":"gg_ve15hqdq_text","default":"<p><strong><u>TargetPoint Massage Therapy</u></strong> has micro-vibration nodes that mimic the hands of a massage therapist, targeting deep knots and tight muscles to release tension, ease stiffness, and promote circulation for faster results.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg4M6gOjnHQ_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg4M6gOjnHQ_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-cbbc74b9-1f18-44dd-a122-288ecd1d5c2b.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggHpBHrYgbf_text","label":"ggHpBHrYgbf_text","default":"<p><strong><u>Thermal Circulation Therapy</u></strong> uses heat to boost rehydration and bring healing nutrients to damaged spinal discs.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggEYNQ-3bio_text","label":"ggEYNQ-3bio_text","default":"<p>Together, these three therapies work to gently decompress your spine and relieve the pressure on your nerves.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>They’re not just masking the pain temporarily, they’re targeting the real issue by restoring space between your vertebrae, rehydrating your discs, and calming the deep inflammation that causes sciatica in the first place.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQhR1IpVck_text","label":"ggQhR1IpVck_text","default":"My Experience Using SmoothSpine Triple Fusion Massager"},{"type":"html","id":"ggwEKdkM7Xr_youtubeUrl","label":"ggwEKdkM7Xr_youtubeUrl","default":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M"},{"type":"html","id":"ggwEKdkM7Xr_vimeoUrl","label":"ggwEKdkM7Xr_vimeoUrl","default":"https://vimeo.com/347119375"},{"type":"html","id":"ggwEKdkM7Xr_html5Url","label":"ggwEKdkM7Xr_html5Url","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/e0112b6395d7442c888c6684ad97b735.mp4"},{"type":"html","id":"ggyt_6ciwbo_text","label":"ggyt_6ciwbo_text","default":"<p>I started with just a 5 minute session and slowly increased the length every few days as my body got used to it.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It felt good knowing I could adjust everything—because every back is different, and having that kind of control made it feel safer and more effective.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>What matters most to me is that the Triple Fusion Massager doesn’t just numb the pain like pills or patches, it actually treats what’s causing it.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>You just lie down, press a button, and it’s like getting a full spinal therapy session without ever leaving your house.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>It’s simple to use, and surprisingly quiet too.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I usually use it while resting in bed or watching my shows in the evening, and it never interrupts anything.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggKNO-EIRnb_text","label":"ggKNO-EIRnb_text","default":"It’s So Easy To Use"},{"type":"html","id":"gg4efinBFB__youtubeUrl","label":"gg4efinBFB__youtubeUrl","default":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M"},{"type":"html","id":"gg4efinBFB__vimeoUrl","label":"gg4efinBFB__vimeoUrl","default":"https://vimeo.com/347119375"},{"type":"html","id":"gg4efinBFB__html5Url","label":"gg4efinBFB__html5Url","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/8892b7af83ce43ebaa948cc51b64698e.mp4"},{"type":"html","id":"ggcu5kkA4Cb_text","label":"ggcu5kkA4Cb_text","default":"<p>All the controls are built right into the top of the device.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Just tap the buttons to choose if you want to go through the automatic program, or manually choose 1 of the 3 therapy styles.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I always start with a setting that feels comfortable, then gradually increase it as my body loosens up, <strong>letting the combination of gentle stretch, targeted massage, and soothing heat take over.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The traction creates space in my spine, and the massage seems to wake up the muscles around it, getting blood flowing and helping everything move the way it should.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Even with just the massage alone, it feels incredible, but once the heat kicks in, it’s like all the stiffness and pressure just melts away. That’s when I really feel the difference.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggNIO8yB_Ji_text","label":"ggNIO8yB_Ji_text","default":"The Science Behind SmoothSpine"},{"type":"html","id":"ggHO14NSlhZ_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggHO14NSlhZ_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-727de96f-a9e8-4038-8526-7127e41159a7.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggHeaxzH-6T_text","label":"ggHeaxzH-6T_text","default":"<p>I was really impressed when I started reading about the research behind these therapies.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Heat relaxes stiff muscles by improving blood flow, and massage helps reduce nerve pressure by loosening tension around the spine.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It’s the combination that makes the Triple Fusion Massager so effective at relieving sciatica and bringing back real mobility.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggrjSqzlPGy_text","label":"ggrjSqzlPGy_text","default":"My Transformation: From Feeling Fragile and Afraid to Standing Tall and Living Again"},{"type":"html","id":"gg9RdTTUKZW_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg9RdTTUKZW_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-cb0fea58-4af0-45ab-b52d-4203605b31c9.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUPrKz2la5_text","label":"ggUPrKz2la5_text","default":"<p>I used to deal with constant pain, stiffness, and nerve flare-ups in my lower back. But after using the Triple Fusion Massager, I can finally say I feel like myself again. No burning, no locking up, and no fear of movement.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The difference is night and day.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg7OWH5i1cb_text","label":"gg7OWH5i1cb_text","default":"<p>Before the Triple Fusion Massager, my life was a nightmare:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggAaby23PEA_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggAaby23PEA_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-4ee35975-73ca-4d69-ab20-3d81af37d4da.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQmZ-m-ifM_text","label":"ggQmZ-m-ifM_text","default":"<p>I couldn’t sit through a meal without shooting pain down my leg</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUCruVTMuv_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggUCruVTMuv_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-4ee35975-73ca-4d69-ab20-3d81af37d4da.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggy4YXIPYCG_text","label":"ggy4YXIPYCG_text","defau